{"tid":2137734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[濱田out]  濱田雅功老婆糊塗播種中國神秘種子","createTime":"2020-08-03T06:58:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T07:57:31.000Z","uid":64191,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"06411dd19fe0ed3910688dea861625167b72caa7","tid":2137734,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T06:58:16.000Z","msg":"日本搞笑藝人、主持人濱田雅功的藝人妻子小川菜摘7月31日在社群發文承認，把從中國大陸寄來的「神祕種子」種進土裡了，看到新聞報導許多人收到一樣的不明包裹，才知鑄下大錯，趕緊處分掉。<br />\n<br />\n小川在部落格及IG發文說，大約一周前接到包裹。以前她曾上網買過植物、種子等，以為這也是網購的植物種子，只是時間太久忘記了，糊里糊塗就播種了。發現是來自中國大陸的可疑種子，才向植物防疫所通報，依指示把種子、發的芽收進兩層袋子處分掉。發文要網友當心。<br />\n<br />\n台灣陸續有民眾收到出貨地址是中國大陸的包裹，裡面裝有培養土、種子等。美國及日本也有民眾接到類似的不明國際包裹。日本農林水產廳指出，有部分像是蔥的種子，但是這些不明來源的種子可能付著有害蟲，呼籲民眾務必通報、不要種植。目前不知道寄件者的用意為何。<br />\n<br />\n「朝日新聞」報導，上月28日住在神奈川的男子收到國際郵件，內有約100個種子，沒有寄件人，但以英文寫著廣東省深圳市，內容物以英文記載「珠寶」。收件人的地址、姓名甚至手機號碼非常完整正確，裡面沒有請款單。<br />\n<br />\n男子說，以為自己網購了什麼東西，於是打開看，曾想過要種子庭院裡，後來覺得可能有危險，改向市公所通報。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6809/4747132\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6809%2F4747132&d=Surr%2FXenqJySG8qcND35%2F%2F3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=2f85b5e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6809/4747132</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/iYkAf3Wz3R8/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FiYkAf3Wz3R8%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=19ba80a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eef571895efdb4e987c7d388f464f7604fdee2e7","tid":2137734,"uid":24345,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T06:59:26.000Z","msg":"浜田應該要公開拍佢老婆個頭一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9195347c86d3f531d9a7026161d50c7faa44994b","tid":2137734,"uid":7043,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T07:01:35.000Z","msg":"冇計既佢又真係有試過上網買種子<br />\n今次個timing 中晒伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abc256a28a6f84152d0e2601eb04d9193c2cc63e","tid":2137734,"uid":40171,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"eef571895efdb4e987c7d388f464f7604fdee2e7","tid":2137734,"uid":24345,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T06:59:26.000Z","msg":"浜田應該要公開拍佢老婆個頭一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T07:12:14.000Z","msg":"直頭要Thai Kick喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e59fb5aba2325c347a0e0094c28b3c2238c9194e","tid":2137734,"uid":89530,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T07:13:48.000Z","msg":"哈媽打 歐多!"},{"pid":"5a55ecd24bd33edc55092bacebcb4adcaae001a6","tid":2137734,"uid":99962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T07:14:51.000Z","msg":"女人就係咁"},{"pid":"05451f055cd170037d4b79a7cdae5e08f6bc6c04","tid":2137734,"uid":190378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T07:15:50.000Z","msg":"田中唔洗Thai kick啦今次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db8055642261a3d5ec13519b14edd0a4bee5e57c","tid":2137734,"uid":321345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T07:16:29.000Z","msg":"笑左<br />\n件事好詼諧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29d5d2aa725149245b4f947187f550fe8a09cc28","tid":2137734,"uid":212246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T07:41:17.000Z","msg":"要好似不準笑咁打屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6543e219a700c88fc4b3cc4ee48366dccc8f05d","tid":2137734,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T07:52:20.000Z","msg":"屌那星，點處理呀？ 唔好就咁丟左佢"},{"pid":"0b045db22479e66f223601327b80e6a3fa10c825","tid":2137734,"uid":59976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T07:57:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/N6NEXN3mYI8/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/t